name: iShares S&P GSCI Commodity-Indexed Trust ETF
short_description: iShares S&P GSCI Commodity-Indexed Trust is an exchange traded fund launched by iShares Delaware Trust Sponsor LLC. The fund is managed by BlackRock Fund Advisors.
long_description: iShares S&P GSCI Commodity-Indexed Trust is an exchange traded fund launched by iShares Delaware Trust Sponsor LLC. The fund is managed by BlackRock Fund Advisors. It invests in commodity markets. The fund invests through derivatives such as futures contracts in a diversified group of physical commodities. It seeks to track the performance of the S&P GSCI Total Return Index. iShares S&P GSCI Commodity-Indexed Trust was formed on July 7, 2006 and is domiciled in the United States.
